OL,7,FA man from Surrey who made his child
OL,8,Fask for permission to use the toilet
OL,9,Fand stand in the corner of the room in
OL,10,Fa stress position has been jailed for
OL,11,Fneglect.
OL,13,FThe man from Addlestone, who can't be
OL,14,Fnamed for legal reasons pleaded guilty
OL,15,Fto offences which took place between
OL,16,FFebruary 2015 and June 2021.
OL,18,FHe's been sentenced to two years and
OL,19,Ffive months in prison at Chichester
OL,20,FCrown Court.
